<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>yǒu yī tiáo xiǎo lù 迦南1044</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 yǒu yī tiáo xiǎo lù, shì rén yǒng bù huì zhī dào.
 yǒu yī tiáo xiǎo lù, fēi niǎo yě bù huì qīng chǔ.
 píng fán de xiǎo lù, liǎng biān zhōng nián zhǎng qīng.
 zhè jiù shì qí dǎo de lù, lù shàng yǒu liáng rén.
 lù shàng yǒu huó shuǐ, lù shàng yǒu ma nǎ, liàng guāng hé ēn huì.
 yuàn shén suǒ yǒu de ér nǚ dōu kàn jiàn zhè yī tiáo xiǎo lù.
 qí dǎo zhī lù, hé děng méng fú.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>1044</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
</song>